| App icon (3D codex, 2048²) | [generated PNG](https://i.mscdn.ai/aafdff66-9114-4d94-847b-8a77449d0598/generated-images/3e917d5c-07f5-4c15-8b2b-649077a6b11c.png) | iOS/macOS icon, App Store, social avatar, splash |
| Favicon glyph | inline SVG above | favicon.svg, in-app nav mark |
| OG image | render from wireframe → `/public/og.png` | meta tag, README hero |

